ecame the Lead Pastors of Portland Christian Center in 2008. &nbsp;Linda is passionate about helping people grow in their walk of faith and spends her time providing simple steps to develop BIG people. Although she is proficient in many counseling and developmental tools she believes that growing in knowledge of Jesus and His ways is at the core of growing as a healthy individual.</p><p>Follow/Contact Pastor Linda Noah: <a href="http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=631758095&amp;ref=ts" class="facebook" target="_blank">Facebook</a> <a href="http://twitter.com/LindaNoah" class="twitter" target="_blank">Twitter</a> <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/lindanoah" class="linkedin" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a> <a href="mailto:lnoah@pcctoday.com" class="email" target="_blank">Email</a></p>